Synnøve Finden bụ ụlọ ọrụ mmiri ara ehi Norwegian nke na-emepụta cheese, bọta na mmiri na ugbo dị na Alvdal na Namsos
Ụlọ ọrụ ahụ wepụtara cheese odo ya na 21 Septemba 1996 na cheese na-acha nchara nchara n'afọ 1997
E depụtara ụlọ ọrụ ahụ na Oslo Stock Exchange
Synnøve Finden bụ taa naanị onye Norway na-ama Tine aka na ahịa cheese Norwegian.
A na-ewere Synnøve Finden (1882-1957) taa dị ka nwanyị mbụ guzobere cheese na onye nwe ụlọ ọrụ
Ya na Pernille Holmen na nwa ya nwanyị Evy (13), Synnøve Finden meghere ụlọ ọrụ cheese mbụ ya na'afọ 1928 na Grefsen Plateau na Oslo
Ọganihu maka mmepụta ahụ bịara mgbe mbụ e webatara cheese ahụ na njikọ ndị inyom ụlọ Hjemmenes Vel
N'afọ 1987, e rere Synnøve Finden A / S na Dag Swanstrøm ma mepụta ya kwaga Enebakk
Site na Swanstrøm kwa, ọganihu (1996) ka ọ bụrụ onye ịma aka na Norwegian Dairies (Tine) na ndị otu ahụ

Na Jenụwarị 1997, Minista Ọrụ Ugbo Gunhild Øyangen sitere na Labour Party kwuru na steeti na otu ndị ọrụ ugbo Norwegian ekwenyela imeghe maka asọmpi na ngalaba mmiri ara ehi.  Na 1995, onye nwe ọhụrụ ahụ gara ịzụrụ mmiri ara ehi Tine mechiri emechi na Alvdal.

Site na oge 1996–2008, Synnøve Fiden abụrụla onye asọmpi Tine nke mbụ nwere chiiz edo edo na brunost.  N'afọ 2008, ụlọ ọrụ ahụ nwetara ndị nwe ọhụrụ, ndị na-emepụta Norwegian Jan Bodd na Stig Sunde.  Afọ iri ka ewegharachara, Karl Kristian Sunde sonye dị ka onye mmekọ na onye nwe ya.
N'afọ 2020, Synnøve Finden gbasaa ahịa ya nke cheese na-acha nchara nchara na South Korea, ebe ereela ihe karịrị Puku iri ise na abuo brunost ka ọ na-erule Mee 2021.
